[]: Re: EoTV Episode 25- an overlooked part in 'the real world'? &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Quote Post by AdamMalkovitch &raquo; Mon Jun 28, 2021 9:34 pm Shinji feeling the start of Instrumentality comes before the eyecatch, this dialogue comes afterwards. Assuming the events shown in ep25 are in chronological order, which makes sense, this would be happening inside Instrumentality during the chaos that ensued immediately following Third Impact, when everyone was confused and terrified, before they became one and settled down [shown in the like 700 different still frames near the end of Komm Susser Tod in EoE]. We have no reason to believe this is an alternate timeline yet, and maybe the series and movie actually are the same timeline but from different perspectives, which is a theme of the TV ending after all.
